ear EFT\nfor the Higgs sector. Finally, we briefly comment on post BICEP2 attempts to\nmodify the Higgs Inflation scenario.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2014 20:29:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Apr 2014 12:47:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 8 May 2014 17:06:57 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 20 Jul 2015 18:19:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-21"}
