sub}}$/M$_\\odot$] respectively for a singular isothermal\nsphere, a pseudo-Jaffe, and an NFW mass profile. This method can extend the\nstudy of flux ratio anomalies to virtually all quadruply imaged quasars, and\ntherefore offers great potential to improve the determination of the subhalo\nmass function in the near future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2014 21:00:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 May 2014 19:21:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
